text: Selling out means giving away one's integrity, morality and principles in exchange for money, 'success' or other personal gain. Some people think that it happens in art when what they think is weird becomes more like mainstream society, so it will make more money. Selling out is seen as getting success at the cost of credibility. == Other websites == *The Art of Selling Out: Compromising the Music Category:Music industry Category:Popular culture
title: Selling out
